# WibeStyle mobile-app environment example.
# Copy to apps/mobile-app/.env for Expo local development.

# API URL visible from the device/emulator.
#
# Android Emulator:
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://10.0.2.2:8080
#
# Physical Android device on the same Wi-Fi:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.10:8080
#
# Production / staging:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.wibestyle.ru

# Notes:
# - 10.0.2.2 is Android Emulator's alias for host machine localhost.
# - If using a physical phone, replace with your Windows LAN IP and make sure
#   firewall allows inbound connections to backend port 8080.
# - OAuth mobile callback scheme is configured in app.config.ts as wibestyle://.
